[0.015, "o", "\u001b[3J\u001b[H\u001b[2J"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1mrocannon\u001b[0m  every installed Ansible module as a typed MCP tool\r\nClaude Haiku driving a real RHEL 9 host in natural language\r\n\r\n"]
[2.003, "o", "\u001b[2m$ rocannon mcp doctor --profile profile-agent.yml\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.911, "o", "[ ok ] tools:              13\r\n[ ok ] resources:          5\r\n"]
[2.078, "o", "\r\n\u001b[2m$ python agent_demo.py\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.446, "o", "connecting to the Rocannon MCP server...\r\n"]
[10.988, "o", "\r\nUSER: What OS and version is host ubi9 running?\r\n"]
[2.869, "o", "  \u001b[33m→\u001b[0m \u001b[1mansible_builtin_setup\u001b[0m  \u001b[2mtarget=ubi9\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.259, "o", "    \u001b[2m↳ status=successful  changed=False\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.488, "o", "  \u001b[36mclaude\u001b[0m  Host **ubi9** is running:\r\n\r\n- **OS**: Red Hat Enterprise Linux (RHEL)\r\n- **Version**: 9.8 (release name: \"Plow\")\r\n- **Major Version**: 9\r\n- **Kernel**: 6.8.0-100-generic\r\n- **Architecture**: aarch64 (ARM 64-bit)\r\n- **Python**: 3.9.25\r\n\r\nAdditional details:\r\n- Virtualized as a Docker container\r\n- 2 vCPU cores with 1959 MB total RAM\r\n- IP Address: 172.17.0.3\r\n"]
[0.043, "o", "\r\nUSER: Run 'uptime' on host ubi9 and report the load averages.\r\n"]
[3.129, "o", "  \u001b[33m→\u001b[0m \u001b[1mansible_builtin_command\u001b[0m  \u001b[2mtarget=ubi9  cmd=uptime\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.760, "o", "    \u001b[2m↳ status=successful  changed=True\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[2.432, "o", "  \u001b[36mclaude\u001b[0m  **Load Averages for host ubi9:**\r\n\r\n- **1-minute**: 0.33\r\n- **5-minute**: 0.34\r\n- **15-minute**: 0.31\r\n\r\n**Additional uptime info:**\r\n- Current time: 18:16:38\r\n- System uptime: 1 day, 18 hours 7 minutes\r\n- Logged-in users: 0\r\n\r\nThe load averages are quite low, indicating the system has minimal load.\r\n"]
[0.050, "o", "\r\nUSER: Set the message of the day on host ubi9 to exactly 'Managed by Rocannon', and tell me whether it changed anything.\r\n"]
[2.603, "o", "  \u001b[33m→\u001b[0m \u001b[1mansible_builtin_copy\u001b[0m  \u001b[2mtarget=ubi9  dest=/etc/motd  content=Managed by Rocannon\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.977, "o", "    \u001b[2m↳ status=successful  changed=False\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[3.032, "o", "  \u001b[36mclaude\u001b[0m  **No changes were made.** ✓\r\n\r\nThe message of the day on host ubi9 was already set to exactly `'Managed by Rocannon'`. The file `/etc/motd` already contained this exact content, so there was nothing to update.\r\n\r\n**File details:**\r\n- Path: `/etc/motd`\r\n- Size: 19 bytes\r\n- Owner: root\r\n- Permissions: 0644\r\n- Status: No modifications needed\r\n"]
